downloadTitle: TaxiNLI: Taking a ride up the NLU Hill
downloadDescription: The data has 22 columns. The pairID points to a unique pair in MultiNLI dev/test set. Genre and label for each sample  is the same as MultiNLI. Annotated Label is annotated by the annotator. Other columns are described in the paper.
